		"description":{
			"value":"<p class=\"subheading\"><b>Power âœ¦ Encounter (Standard Action)</b></p><p><b>Effect</b>: You cause the decanter to pour forth fresh or salt water in one of three volumes.</p><p><b>* Stream</b>: 1 gallon.</p><p><b>* Fountain</b>: 5 gallons in a 5-foot-long stream.</p><p><b>* Geyser</b>: 30 gallons in a 20-foot-long stream.</p><p>In addition to filling a container of suitable volume, the fountain function of the decanter can be used to clear dirt or light debris from an area 2 squares on a side. The geyser function can be used to break a door or other object. If you do, you gain a +5 power bonus to the check. The area in a burst 1 centered on the door or object is difficult terrain until the end of the encounter. However, the geyser creates considerable pressure, and you must succeed on a DC 16 Strength check when you use it or be knocked prone.</p>",
